---
title: Roasted Shawarma-Spiced Chicken Thighs and Bulgur with Tomato-Herb Salad and Lemon-Garlic Toum
description: Fresh, aromatic flavours meet tender spiced chicken in this delicious dish, inspired by one of our favourite take-out meals. A hearty bed of savoury bulgur and roasted peppers turns it into a wholesome weeknight feast!
